      "notes": "\nYour problematic favs are leaving \ud83d\udeeb\n\nThe rumours are true. After years of unsolicited opinions, questionable group chat takes, and being suspiciously well-informed about everyone's business, Martha and Stan are finally being deported from Denmark.\n\nMartha is off to LSE to explain to Londoners how things actually work. Stan is off to the College of Europe, where he will continue being insufferable about EU institutions.\n\nThis is your last chance to:\n- Settle any unfinished beef\n- Get one final hot take you didn't ask for\n- Pretend you'll visit (you won't)\n- Witness us cry at least once before midnight\n\nBring yourself, bring a drink (or dont we have a kollegium bar), bring receipts. \n\nDress code: come as you are!\n\nSee you there before we become someone else's problem. \ud83d\udc94",
